Periodic elements table

Please note that these tools aren't optimized for large amounts of data, processing can slow down or run into problems once you reach above 150,000 characters. A cap of 1 million characters is currently in place.

Periodic elements

An interactive periodic table of elements, click each element to display a table of related information. Not in the usual format, as creating a scalable grid in the same shape just didn't seem feasible.

There is more information available on the Periodic table wikipedia page.

— Data sourced from Bowserinator / Periodic-Table-JSON under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 License.
